  <brief_title>Foster 100/6 mg NEXThaler Versus Foster 100/6mg Pressurized Metered-dose Inhaler (pMDI) in Patients With Controlled Asthma.</brief_title>
  <acronym>FORTUNE</acronym>
  <official_title>A 12-week, Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind, Double-dummy, 2-arm Parallel Group Study Comparing the Efficacy and Safety of Foster 100/6mg NEXThaler, 2 Inhalations b.i.d, Versus Foster 100/6mg pMDI, 2 Puffs b.i.d in Patients With Controlled Asthma</official_title>
