  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to demonstrate the non-inferiority of Foster 100/6mg NEXThaler
      versus Foster 100/6mg pMDI in terms of pulmonary function in asthmatic patients, as well as
      the effect of the test treatments in terms of additional lung function parameters and
      clinical outcome measures. The purpose is also to assess the safety and tolerability.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
